data.description:
**VA Assumable Loan**
Experience vibrant living in our newest community tailored for those aged 55 and better – The Reserve. This remarkable enclave is set to deliver an exclusive 10,000 sq. ft. amenity center, a refreshing outdoor pool, and so much more. Your personal Lifestyle Director will nurture your resort-style living.

Introducing The Douglas plan by Oakwood Homes, meticulously designed with your needs in mind. This residence features a luxurious master suite, a secondary bedroom, and convenient main-floor laundry. Get ready to host and entertain in the expansive great room or transition to the dining area and gourmet-style kitchen complete with a generously sized granite eat-in island. The kitchen is a chef's dream, and a covered outdoor patio is just steps away, making it perfect for gatherings.

Don't let this fantastic opportunity to reside in this highly sought-after home pass you by. Welcome to a new chapter of comfortable and stylish living at The Reserve.

**This property may qualify for a $5,000 Chase Homebuyer Grant that can be used to reduce the cost of your Chase mortgage. For more information contact, Darrel J Clark II , NMLS 1307528 at 303-901-9121 orDarrel.j.Clark@Chase.com.
